author: pamarcelot
msg: Updated the Maven Studio Plugin to handle correctly the version of an artifact.
This will transform the version in a valid OSGI version.
This fix is need is we want to use snapshot version (i.e. 1.3.0-SNAPSHOT) which is not a valid OSGI identifier (it will be renamed as 1.3.0.SNAPSHOT).
